    "title": "Passed Pawn",
    "pageid": 1476,
    "redirects": [],
    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a> * <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">Pawn Structure</a> * Passed Pawn</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:274px;\"><a href=\"http://www.freibauer-schoeneberg.de/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/2/22/LOGO_SC_Freibauer_Schoneberg.jpg\" width=\"272\" height=\"271\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:LOGO_SC_Freibauer_Schoneberg.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Schachclub <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freibauer_%28Schach%29\">Freibauer</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sch%C3%B6neberg\">Schöneberg</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p>A <b>passed pawn,</b> also called <b>free pawn</b> or <b>passer</b>, is a <a href=\"/Pawn\" title=\"Pawn\">pawn</a> with no opponent pawns in front on the same or adjacent files. In case of <a href=\"/Doubled_Pawn\" title=\"Doubled Pawn\">doubled pawns</a>, it is wrong to score the back twin as passed, even if it meets the above conditions. Therefor, the passer requires his <a href=\"/Pawn_Spans\" title=\"Pawn Spans\">front span</a> <a href=\"/General_Setwise_Operations#DisjointSets\" title=\"General Setwise Operations\">disjoint</a> from all other pawns, as well as the <a href=\"/Pawn_Fills\" title=\"Pawn Fills\">front fill</a> disjoint from opponent pawn attacks, which also excludes <a href=\"/Pawn_Levers_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Pawn Levers (Bitboards)\">pawn levers</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Considerations\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Considerations</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#1998_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1998 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Considerations\">Considerations</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Passed_Pawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Considerations\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>In its simplest form, passed pawn evaluation assigns a bonus which increases as the pawn advances, often by dedicated <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">piece-square tables</a>. There are, however, different considerations to be taken into account, some of which are listed below. \n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Blockade_of_Stop\" title=\"Blockade of Stop\">Blockade of Stop</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Control_of_Stop_and_Telestop\" title=\"Control of Stop and Telestop\">Control of Stop and Telestop</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Connected_Passed_Pawns\" title=\"Connected Passed Pawns\">Connected Passed Pawns</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Pawn_Tropism\" title=\"King Pawn Tropism\">King Pawn Tropism</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Outside_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Outside Passed Pawn\">Outside Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Race\" title=\"Pawn Race\">Pawn Race</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Protected_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Protected Passed Pawn\">Protected Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Rule_of_the_Square\" title=\"Rule of the Square\">Rule of the Square</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tarrasch_Rule\" title=\"Tarrasch Rule\">Tarrasch Rule</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Unstoppable_Passer\" title=\"Unstoppable Passer\">Unstoppable Passer</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Passed_Pawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Candidate_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Candidate Passed Pawn\">Candidate Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hidden_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Hidden Passed Pawn\">Hidden Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Passed_Pawns_(Bitboards)\" title=\"Passed Pawns (Bitboards)\">Passed Pawns (Bitboards)</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn_Extensions\" title=\"Passed Pawn Extensions\">Passed Pawn Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawns_Breakthrough\" title=\"Pawns Breakthrough\">Pawns Breakthrough</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Promotions\" title=\"Promotions\">Promotions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/R%C3%A9ti_Endgame_Study\" title=\"Réti Endgame Study\">Réti Endgame Study</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Pattern#SetwiseRuleoftheSquare\" title=\"King Pattern\">Set-wise Rule of the Square</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Passed_Pawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1998_...\">1998 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Passed_Pawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 1998 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=17661\">Passed Pawn Evaluation</a> by <a href=\"/Stuart_Cracraft\" title=\"Stuart Cracraft\">Stuart Cracraft</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=75113\">Passed pawn values</a> by <a href=\"/James_Robertson\" title=\"James Robertson\">James Robertson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 27, 1999</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Passed_Pawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=98943\">Passed Pawn Suite</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Howard_Exner&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Howard Exner (page does not exist)\">Howard Exner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 24, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Test-Positions\" title=\"Test-Positions\">Test-Positions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=290374\">Intersting testposition: multiple passed pawns</a> by <a href=\"/Alex_Kure\" title=\"Alex Kure\">Alexander Kure</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 23, 2003</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=341706\">passed pawn evaluation</a> by macaroni, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 11, 2004</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Passed_Pawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34198\">Passed Pawns (endgame)</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Marek_Kwiatkowski&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Marek Kwiatkowski (page does not exist)\">Marek Kwiatkowski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 07, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34879\">An unstoppable passed pawn</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Marek_Kwiatkowski&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Marek Kwiatkowski (page does not exist)\">Marek Kwiatkowski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 11, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37748\">Improving evaluation of passed pawns</a> by <a href=\"/Ben-Hur_Carlos_Vieira_Langoni_Junior\" title=\"Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Junior\">Ben-Hur Carlos Vieira Langoni Junior</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 22, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Candidate_Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Candidate Passed Pawn\">Candidate Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48823\">passed pawn question</a> by <a href=\"/Alberto_Sanjuan\" title=\"Alberto Sanjuan\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 02, 2013</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Passed_Pawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55392\">The strongest passer</a> by <a href=\"/Lyudmil_Tsvetkov\" title=\"Lyudmil Tsvetkov\">Lyudmil Tsvetkov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 19, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55433\">bad eval for passers&#160;?</a> by <a href=\"/Daniel_Anulliero\" title=\"Daniel Anulliero\">Daniel Anulliero</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 23, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56682\">passed but doubled pawns</a> by <a href=\"/Jon_Dart\" title=\"Jon Dart\">Jon Dart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 15, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Doubled_Pawn\" title=\"Doubled Pawn\">Doubled Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57708\">Passed pawn detection in array based board representations</a> by <a href=\"/Shawn_Chidester\" title=\"Shawn Chidester\">Shawn Chidester</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 20, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58583\">Passed pawn evaluation</a> by <a href=\"/Daniel_Mehrmann\" title=\"Daniel Mehrmann\">Daniel Mehrmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 13, 2015</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Passed_Pawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Passed_pawn\">Passed pawn from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.top10chess.com/2008/09/tactical-motif-iv-passed-pawns.html\">Top 10 chess: Tactical Motif IV: Passed pawns &amp; Promotions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://webspace.utexas.edu/zzw57/rtc/eval/passed_pawns.html\">Passed Pawn Evaluation</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://webspace.utexas.edu/zzw57/rtc/eval/eval.html\">Rybka 1.0 beta vs. Fruit Evaluation</a> by <a href=\"/Zach_Wegner\" title=\"Zach Wegner\">Zach Wegner</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Rybka_Controversy\" title=\"Rybka Controversy\">Rybka Controversy</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Passed_Pawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.freibauer-schoeneberg.de/\">Schachclub Freibauer Schöneberg e.V</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_r